[normal]welcomes the opportunity to 
[normal]respond to the House of Commons Select Committee inquiry on the UK’s Development Work in the Middle East. SACH 
[normal]is an international, non-g
[normal]overnmental, non-political, 
[normal]non-profit
[normal] organization founded in 
[normal]1996 in
[normal] Holon, Israel 
[normal]at the Wolfson Medical 
[normal]Centre
