[normal]centres
[normal] of com
[normal]petence in these countries. 
[normal]SACH is fully dedicated to the idea that every child deserves the best medical treatment available, regardless of the child's nationality, religion, race, gender or financial situation. 
[normal]Due to the fact that over 50% of the child
[normal]ren, who receive cardiac care from SACH, reside in the West Bank and Gaza, it is of significance for SACH
[normal] to respond to this inquiry.
